# Framework-owned cache (type defs, SCSS tokens, fonts, component lib).
# Regenerated from ../zero.toml via `zero update -y`. Never hand-edit.
# Anchored (leading slash) so it matches ONLY web/.zero — the framework cache —
# and NOT web/dist/.zero, whose fonts are part of the committed built UI.
/.zero/
# NOTE: web/dist/ is intentionally NOT ignored. The built UI is a committed
# artifact so cubby builds with a Rust toolchain alone (no `zero` on the build
# path). Regenerate it with `zero build` and commit the result before pushing.
# See docs/features/distribution-spec.md.
# Test / mutation reports.
coverage/
mutation/
